reviewText:
The dvd set looked interesting so I bought it.  Mazinkaiser is from my childhood.  I vaguely remember the  American version of this.  I haven't watched Shuten Doji yet but I will.

If you like anime, you will like these.
It went well! My request was well protected and came as wanted, without any damage! I am very pleased! I must say that I recommend! Thanks
